snippet.title: Raiden IV x MIKADO remix Gameplay | Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Gameplay for Raiden IV x MIKADO remix on Switch (shown here), PlayStation 5, PlayStation 4, Xbox Series X, and Xbox One.

Raiden IV has been around for well over a decade and it now has a brand new iteration for Nintendo Switch that's chock full of content. Full review - https://videochums.com/review/raiden-iv-x-mikado-remix
